/*******************************************************************************
* Pauses chr->timer60 (does not reset value)                                   *
********************************************************************************
* Notes: Local timer is different to hud countdown.                            *
*       Local timer is unique for each chr, while hud countdown is global for  *
*       the entire mission.                                                    *
